        <div1 type="body">
            


<p><placeName>Jefferson Saline County [Missouri]</placeName> <date when="1821-12-03">Decr 3rd 1821</date></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>By the Opportunity of <persName>Dr G. C. Hartt</persName> I write you a few lines,
wishing you to give me what information you may think worth 
attention respecting your new Country, also what arraingments are
made respecting our business in this state&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>Dr Hartt</persName> is on an exploring expedition to your Section of the
<placeName>Country </placeName>and means to live there if he likes it better than this, I
have some notion of removing there if he does, believeing this state
too cold any information you can give him respecting the Country
will be thankfully acknowledged by</p>
<p>Yours respectfully</p>

<p><persName>George Tennill[e]</persName></p>
<p><persName>Stephen F Austin Esqr</persName></p>

        </div1>
